{
  "stem": "23645.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because the danger was-- there were no kids to speak of.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There were-- I think there was two or three.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But in my section, I was the only one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I was doing work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was very secure at work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I was useful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Nazis, the Gestapo, looked at me and, good worker.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We like this, this guy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I wasn't a child to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was doing something useful to the German machinery.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The problem was going to the barracks to sleep, which means we had to walk a distance.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we were counted, I could be discovered.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was never in the front, I was always-- you stay inside, so they won't notice you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And life went on that way, and I was pretty secure.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was quite happy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At first it was kind of tough doing this, because every time I lifted one of these shells-- they weren't extremely heavy but heavy enough that it rubbed the skin off my fingers.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so I'm told they toughened up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had bandages all over the place because of a-- the skin were rubbed off, and they were bleeding quite heavily.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I had a little problem at first, but then they hardened up, and I was just away to the races.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the end of the shift, we would go to the barracks to sleep.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was another agony.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We slept in these, these bunks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nothing but straw on it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were no, no mattresses or anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We slept [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in our clothes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't change, we didn't-- there wasn't such a thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the lice were just horrendous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were bed bugs.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
